{"tid":1176426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉恐嚇殺前女友父母 控方堅持檢控拒簽保了事","createTime":"2019-05-29T08:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T08:34:05.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4495e594da2d4e7b0abc0a17052e00acabe5c640","tid":1176426,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSDcno0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSDcno0.png&h=d869e037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告許劍霆。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n現役警員疑因不忿女友提出分手，涉嫌先後發送WhatsApp訊息及在對方IG留言，揚言會於她的住所門外放火，殺死她的父母，令她永遠沒有屋企人。涉案警員被控刑事恐嚇罪，案件早前提訊時，主任裁判官練錦鴻提出案件應可以簽保守行為方式處理，並謂「不能因為職業而歧視」。惟案件押後至今日再訊時，控方表明決定維持檢控。<br />\n<br />\n被告許劍霆（22歲）被控於去年10月16日至17日，在香港威脅一名女士，會使其父母人身安全受損害。被告今否認控罪，案件押後至6月12日開審，控方將傳召6名證人。被告獲准繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：STCC1816/19】<br />\n記者羅日昇"},{"pid":"77b7c008c9e2429b99a395639989e778e98e95ee","tid":1176426,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"警警相衛"},{"pid":"0b5def70230185ffcc658d93b89512c432e72cb9","tid":1176426,"uid":71824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:26:22.000Z","msg":"等坐監啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9b103c02b38645adbbbe8cb6d8eb0cf2d4ebc6","tid":1176426,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"主任裁判官練錦鴻提出案件應可以簽保守行為方式處理<br />\n老妨?"},{"pid":"87088b7303816251afb7ec9c1193401ab365b9cb","tid":1176426,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"22歲"},{"pid":"ae65c20bdee3db7eeb0f8364ccb51211a051aaed","tid":1176426,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"想問下告人既係咪律政司？"}]}